-- Cristiano Ronaldo Wants to Return to Manchester Utd., Sun Says
-- B y   G r a n t   S m i t h
-- 2012-12-23T09:28:51Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-12-23/cristiano-ronaldo-wants-to-return-to-manchester-utd-sun-says.html
Real  Madrid ’s Cristiano Ronaldo
wants to return to Manchester United, the Sun reported, citing a
friend of the soccer player who wasn’t identified.  Manchester United’s manager, Alex Ferguson, had signaled
earlier his desire to hire Ronaldo, who played for the team from
2003 to 2009, according to the Sun.  To contact the reporter on this story:
